The '''Lorrd Logistician Liberation League''' was a radical student group on [[Lorrd/Legends|Lorrd]] around [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. They sought to overthrow the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] government and replace it with ruthlessly analytical and pragmatic [[Computer/Legends|computers]].

